summary:
I don’t post very often...usually just between working and sleeping and seeing my husband. 
But I must say that getting on my...
body:
I don’t post very often…usually just between working and sleeping and seeing my husband.

But I must say that getting on my tswift-dedicated tumblr is so much fun for me…seeing everyone’s theories and seeing that I’m not the only one making certain connections!


A lot of people I know don’t like Taylor’s music and really just don’t get the whole “theory” “Easter egg” “guess what Taylor’s up to today” game that we play…so getting to come online and interact with y’all makes some of the days when maybe I don’t get to see my husband, or mornings when I’ve had not-so-good nights at work better.


I’m so grateful for such a fun outlet in my life @taylorswift. Thank you for creating this fandom ☺️

….23 and still growing up now ❣️
